pr_title: Extended Deps Worker to Collect Scorecard Data
pr_body:
Extended Deps Worker to collect Scorecard Data - 

Things I have changed - 
Installation Scripts 
added a check that if 'go' package exists to run scorecard.
Added script to check if scorecard exists already, if not clone and build 
in Deps worker used Subprocess to call scorecard and made necessary env settings

pr_body:
The Worker is currently supporting PYPI package manager only, with files setup.py, requirement.txt, Pipfile, Pipfile.lock. I also have added a parser for Poetry which has some bugs. So for now it is commented out and the worker doesn't act on poetry files.

Added new Schema V62 which introduces repo_deps_libyear table.

Added a new dependency in setup.py - "toml"

I would be soon adding support for other package managers as well.

pr_title: Added Conda support for libyear Worker
pr_body:
Pip dependencies can be embedded in conda environment files, so added a parser for that
This completes all the parsers for PYPI
This also introduces a new dependency in setup.py - 'pyYaml' to parse conda environment YAML files
